Package: funcml
Type: Package
Title: Functional Machine Learning with Formula-First API
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Imad", family = "El Badisy", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "elbadisyimad@gmail.com")
  )
Author: Imad El Badisy [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Imad El Badisy <elbadisyimad@gmail.com>
Description: Functional machine learning toolkit with a formula-first interface.
    Provides a compact, explicit, formula-first modeling workflow built around
    thin S3 wrappers for base learners and popular engines using functional
    composition via the functionals package. Includes evaluation, tuning,
    interpretability, learner comparison, and plug-in g-computation utilities
    with ggplot2 visualizations. The package is intentionally opinionated:
    preprocessing is expected to happen outside the modeling step, and the
    framework focuses on a compact cross-validation-centered workflow rather
    than competing feature for feature with larger machine learning ecosystems.
